SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT A.[Tgl SO], A.[No SO], A.[Nama Customers], A.[Nama Barang], A.[Jumlah Bag], A.[Jumlah Kg], A.Harga, A.TOTAL, A.[Sisa SO], B.[Tgl DO], B.[No DO], B.[Jumlah Bag], C.[Tgl Invoice], C.[No Invoice], C.[Jumlah Bag], C.[Jumlah Kg], C.Discount, C.TOTAL, D.[Tgl Terima Uang], D.[Bukti Terima Uang], D.TOTAL, C.[Sisa Piutang] FROM (SELECT A1.DocEntry, LineNum, A1.ObjType, A.DocDate AS 'Tgl SO', CASE WHEN A.DocNum IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT('SO-', A.U_IDU_Kode_PT, '-', CAST(A.DocNum AS varchar(10))) ELSE '' END AS 'No SO', A.CardCode, A.CardName AS 'Nama Customers', A1.ItemCode, A1.Dscription AS 'Nama Barang', A1.U_IDU_QtyPack AS 'Jumlah Bag', A1.Quantity 'Jumlah Kg', A1.PriceBefDi AS Harga, (A1.Quantity * A1.PriceBefDi) AS TOTAL, A1.OpenQty AS 'Sisa SO', A.U_IDU_Kode_PT FROM RDR1 AS A1 JOIN ORDR AS A ON A.DocEntry = A1.DocEntry AND A.CANCELED = 'N') A FULL OUTER JOIN (SELECT A1.DocEntry, LineNum, A1.ObjType, A1.BaseEntry, A1.BaseLine, A1.BaseType, A.DocDate AS 'Tgl DO', CASE WHEN A.DocNum IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT('DO-', A.U_IDU_Kode_PT, '-', CAST(A.DocNum AS varchar(10))) ELSE '' END AS 'No DO', A1.U_IDU_QtyPack AS 'Jumlah Bag' FROM DLN1 AS A1 JOIN ODLN AS A ON A.DocEntry = A1.DocEntry AND A.CANCELED = 'N') B ON A.DocEntry = B.BaseEntry AND A.LineNum = B.BaseLine AND A.ObjType = B.BaseType FULL OUTER JOIN (SELECT A1.DocEntry, LineNum, A1.BaseEntry, A1.BaseLine, A1.BaseType, A1.ObjType, A.DocDate AS 'Tgl Invoice', CASE WHEN A.DocNum IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT('INV-', A.U_IDU_Kode_PT, '-', CAST(A.DocNum AS varchar(10))) ELSE '' END AS 'No Invoice', A1.U_IDU_QtyPack AS 'Jumlah Bag', A1.Quantity 'Jumlah Kg', A1.PriceBefDi AS Harga, (A1.Quantity * A1.PriceBefDi * (A1.DiscPrcnt / 100)) AS Discount, (A1.Quantity * A1.PriceBefDi) AS TOTAL, A.DocTotal - A.PaidToDate AS 'Sisa Piutang' FROM INV1 AS A1 JOIN OINV AS A ON A.DocEntry = A1.DocEntry AND A.CANCELED = 'N') C ON B.DocEntry = C.BaseEntry AND B.LineNum = C.BaseLine AND B.ObjType = C.BaseType LEFT JOIN (SELECT baseAbs, invtype, A.DocDate AS 'Tgl Terima Uang', CONCAT('BT-', A1.OcrCode, '-', CAST(A.DocNum AS varchar(10))) AS 'Bukti Terima Uang', A1.SumApplied AS TOTAL FROM RCT2 AS A1 JOIN ORCT AS A ON A1.DocNum = A.DocEntry AND A.Canceled = 'N') D ON C.DocEntry = D.baseAbs AND C.ObjType = D.InvType WHERE A.[Tgl SO] BETWEEN ':1' AND ':2' AND (A.ItemCode = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') AND (A.CardCode = ':4' or ':4' is null or ':4' = '') AND (A.U_IDU_Kode_PT = ':5' or ':5' is null or ':5' = '') order by a.DocEntry,a.LineNum,b.DocEntry,b.LineNum,c.DocEntry,c.LineNum

SELECT A.LineNum, A.[Tgl SO], A.[No SO], A.[Nama Customers], A.[Nama Barang], A.[Jumlah Bag], A.[Jumlah Kg], A.Harga, a.DocCur, A.TOTAL, A.[Sisa SO], B.[Tgl DO], B.[No DO],b.LineNum, B.[Jumlah Bag],B.Quantity, C.[Tgl Invoice],C.LineNum, C.[No Invoice], C.[Jumlah Bag], C.[Jumlah Kg], c.Harga, C.Discount, C.TOTAL, D.[Tgl Terima Uang], D.[Bukti Terima Uang], D.TOTAL, C.[Sisa Piutang] FROM (SELECT A1.DocEntry, LineNum, A1.ObjType, A.DocDate AS 'Tgl SO', CASE WHEN A.DocNum IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT('SO-', A.U_IDU_Kode_PT, '-', CAST(A.DocNum AS varchar(15))) ELSE '' END AS 'No SO', A.CardCode, A.CardName AS 'Nama Customers', A1.ItemCode, A1.Dscription AS 'Nama Barang', A1.U_IDU_QtyPack AS 'Jumlah Bag', A1.Quantity 'Jumlah Kg', A1.PriceBefDi AS Harga, (A1.Quantity * A1.PriceBefDi) AS TOTAL, A1.OpenQty AS 'Sisa SO', A.U_IDU_Kode_PT, a.DocCur FROM RDR1 AS A1 JOIN ORDR AS A ON A.DocEntry = A1.DocEntry AND A.CANCELED = 'N') A FULL OUTER JOIN (SELECT A1.DocEntry, LineNum, A1.ObjType, A1.BaseEntry, A1.BaseLine, A1.BaseType, A.DocDate AS 'Tgl DO', CASE WHEN A.DocNum IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT('DO-', A.U_IDU_Kode_PT, '-', CAST(A.DocNum AS varchar(15))) ELSE '' END AS 'No DO', A1.U_IDU_QtyPack AS 'Jumlah Bag',A1.Quantity FROM DLN1 AS A1 JOIN ODLN AS A ON A.DocEntry = A1.DocEntry AND A.CANCELED = 'N') B ON A.DocEntry = B.BaseEntry AND A.LineNum = B.BaseLine AND A.ObjType = B.BaseType FULL OUTER JOIN (SELECT A1.DocEntry, LineNum, A1.BaseEntry, A1.BaseLine, A1.BaseType, A1.ObjType, A.DocDate AS 'Tgl Invoice', CASE WHEN A.DocNum IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT('INV-', A.U_IDU_Kode_PT, '-', CAST(A.DocNum AS varchar(15))) ELSE '' END AS 'No Invoice', A1.U_IDU_QtyPack AS 'Jumlah Bag', A1.Quantity 'Jumlah Kg', A1.PriceBefDi AS Harga, (A1.Quantity * A1.PriceBefDi * (A1.DiscPrcnt / 100)) AS Discount, (A1.Quantity * A1.PriceBefDi) AS TOTAL, A.DocTotal - A.PaidToDate AS 'Sisa Piutang' FROM INV1 AS A1 JOIN OINV AS A ON A.DocEntry = A1.DocEntry AND A.CANCELED = 'N') C ON B.DocEntry = C.BaseEntry AND B.LineNum = C.BaseLine AND B.ObjType = C.BaseType LEFT JOIN (SELECT baseAbs, invtype, A.DocDate AS 'Tgl Terima Uang', CONCAT('BT-', A1.OcrCode, '-', CAST(A.DocNum AS varchar(15))) AS 'Bukti Terima Uang', A1.SumApplied AS TOTAL FROM RCT2 AS A1 JOIN ORCT AS A ON A1.DocNum = A.DocEntry AND A.Canceled = 'N') D ON C.DocEntry = D.baseAbs AND C.ObjType = D.InvType WHERE A.[Tgl SO] BETWEEN ':1' AND ':2' AND (A.ItemCode = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') AND (A.CardCode = ':4' or ':4' is null or ':4' = '') AND (A.U_IDU_Kode_PT = ':5' or ':5' is null or ':5' = '') order by a.DocEntry,a.LineNum,b.DocEntry,b.LineNum,c.DocEntry,c.LineNum
